name: Skid Row Development Corp
review_text:

The floor plan is one room with a bed, refrigerator, no sink, and maybe a table chair is provided.
In maintaining the health of the environment, the tenants and guests smoke in the building. Such as in their room, hallway, and bathrooms arias.
